    "summary":  "Implement Phase 2D Promotion Determinism Guard for LCS promotion replay safety: enforce one-emission-one-CID via cid_intake(emission_id) uniqueness, make fn_promote_emission idempotent with conflict-safe return behavior, and harden batch promotion for concurrency with FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED and no double-minting under parallel workers.",
